    <item>
      <title>Add bot: to a group chat</title>
      <link>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-to-groupchat/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-to-groupchat/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 1: Invoke &amp;ldquo;Get bots&amp;rdquo; menu&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-1-invoke-get-bots-menu&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-1-invoke-get-bots-menu&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In a group chat, start a message with a &lt;code&gt;@&lt;/code&gt;, wait for the menu to pop and select &amp;ldquo;Get bots&amp;rdquo;
&lt;img src=&#34;0100-add-to-groupchat.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 2: Invite Notifier&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-2-invite-notifier&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-2-invite-notifier&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the popup, search for &lt;strong&gt;Notifier&lt;/strong&gt; and select it.
&lt;img src=&#34;0110-add-app-to-group-chat.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Stop 3: PM with the token&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;stop-3-pm-with-the-token&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#stop-3-pm-with-the-token&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;As you added the bot to the group chat, you&amp;rsquo;ll receive a private message from the bot with a &lt;code&gt;conversation_token&lt;/code&gt; for this very conversation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;0020-groupchat.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;0030-unnamed-groupchat.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Add bot: to a channel</title>
      <link>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-to-channel/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-to-channel/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        




  












&lt;div class=&#34;hx-overflow-x-auto hx-mt-6 hx-flex hx-rounded-lg hx-border hx-py-2 ltr:hx-pr-4 rtl:hx-pl-4 contrast-more:hx-border-current contrast-more:dark:hx-border-current hx-border-yellow-100 hx-bg-yellow-50 hx-text-yellow-900 dark:hx-border-yellow-200/30 dark:hx-bg-yellow-700/30 dark:hx-text-yellow-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;ltr:hx-pl-3 ltr:hx-pr-2 rtl:hx-pr-3 rtl:hx-pl-2&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hx-select-none hx-text-xl&#34; style=&#34;font-family: &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;&#34;&gt;
        ⚠️
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-w-full hx-min-w-0 hx-leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-6 hx-leading-7 first:hx-mt-0&#34;&gt;
      Apps can only be added to public channels
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 1: Invoke &amp;ldquo;Get bots&amp;rdquo; menu&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-1-invoke-get-bots-menu&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-1-invoke-get-bots-menu&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;If the bot is not present in the team, in the channel, start a message with a &lt;code&gt;@&lt;/code&gt;, wait for the menu to pop and select &amp;ldquo;Get bots&amp;rdquo;
&lt;img src=&#34;invoke-get-bot-menu.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 2: Invite Notifier&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-2-invite-notifier&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-2-invite-notifier&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the popup, search for &lt;em&gt;Notifier&lt;/em&gt; and select it
&lt;img src=&#34;search-for-notifier.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx-overflow-x-auto hx-mt-6 hx-flex hx-rounded-lg hx-border hx-py-2 ltr:hx-pr-4 rtl:hx-pl-4 contrast-more:hx-border-current contrast-more:dark:hx-border-current hx-border-blue-200 hx-bg-blue-100 hx-text-blue-900 dark:hx-border-blue-200/30 dark:hx-bg-blue-900/30 dark:hx-text-blue-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;ltr:hx-pl-3 ltr:hx-pr-2 rtl:hx-pr-3 rtl:hx-pl-2&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hx-select-none hx-text-xl&#34; style=&#34;font-family: &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;&#34;&gt;
        ℹ️
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-w-full hx-min-w-0 hx-leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-6 hx-leading-7 first:hx-mt-0&#34;&gt;
      if there is no reaction, no private message, the bot might have already been added, just follow &lt;a href=&#34;https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/get-a-token/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Get a token&lt;/a&gt; instructions.
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Add bot: the generic way</title>
      <link>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-generic/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/add-bot-generic/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 1: Open the App tab&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-1-open-the-app-tab&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-1-open-the-app-tab&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In MS Teams left panel, click the &lt;em&gt;Apps&lt;/em&gt; tab
&lt;img src=&#34;app-tab.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 2: Search for &lt;em&gt;Notifier&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-2-search-for-notifier&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-2-search-for-notifier&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the popup, search for &lt;em&gt;Notifier&lt;/em&gt; and select it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx-overflow-x-auto hx-mt-6 hx-flex hx-rounded-lg hx-border hx-py-2 ltr:hx-pr-4 rtl:hx-pl-4 contrast-more:hx-border-current contrast-more:dark:hx-border-current hx-border-red-200 hx-bg-red-100 hx-text-red-900 dark:hx-border-red-200/30 dark:hx-bg-red-900/30 dark:hx-text-red-200&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;ltr:hx-pl-3 ltr:hx-pr-2 rtl:hx-pr-3 rtl:hx-pl-2&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hx-select-none hx-text-xl&#34; style=&#34;font-family: &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;&#34;&gt;
        🚫
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-w-full hx-min-w-0 hx-leading-7&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-6 hx-leading-7 first:hx-mt-0&#34;&gt;
      Do not click open button, click the app card
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;search-notifier-app.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 3: Choose where to add the bot&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-3-choose-where-to-add-the-bot&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-3-choose-where-to-add-the-bot&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Click the down arrow and choose to &lt;em&gt;Add to a team&lt;/em&gt; or &lt;em&gt;Add to a chat&lt;/em&gt;.
&lt;img src=&#34;0040-easy-to-add.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 4: Add to the desired conversation&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-4-add-to-the-desired-conversation&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-4-add-to-the-desired-conversation&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-scrollbar hx-overflow-x-auto hx-overflow-y-hidden hx-overscroll-x-contain&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-4 hx-flex hx-w-max hx-min-w-full hx-border-b hx-border-gray-200 hx-pb-px dark:hx-border-neutral-800&#34;&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;  tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34;&gt;to a Group Chat&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;&gt;to a Team&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34; &gt;Select the group chat and click &lt;em&gt;Set up a bot&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;0050-add-to-a-groupchat.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;Select the team and click &lt;em&gt;Set up a bot&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;0050-add-to-a-team.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Get a token</title>
      <link>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/get-a-token/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://teams-notifier.github.io/docs/user-manual/get-a-token/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;div class=&#34;steps hx-ml-4 hx-mb-12 ltr:hx-border-l rtl:hx-border-r hx-border-gray-200 ltr:hx-pl-6 rtl:hx-pr-6 dark:hx-border-neutral-800 [counter-reset:step]&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 1: Highligh the Bot&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-1-highligh-the-bot&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-1-highligh-the-bot&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the conversation for which you want a token, highlight the bot by posting a message with &lt;code&gt;@notifier&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-scrollbar hx-overflow-x-auto hx-overflow-y-hidden hx-overscroll-x-contain&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-4 hx-flex hx-w-max hx-min-w-full hx-border-b hx-border-gray-200 hx-pb-px dark:hx-border-neutral-800&#34;&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;  tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34;&gt;in a Group Chat&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;&gt;in a Team&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34; &gt;In the message input, start typing &lt;code&gt;@notifier&lt;/code&gt;, select the proposition, your typed text should be converted in purple text then post the message
&lt;img src=&#34;groupchat-highlight-bot.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;In the message part of the editor (not the subject), start typing &lt;code&gt;@notifier&lt;/code&gt;, select the proposition, your typed text should be converted in purple text then post the message
&lt;img src=&#34;channel-highlight-bot.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 2: Get a token&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-2-get-a-token&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-2-get-a-token&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bot will reply with a card, click the card or the &lt;em&gt;Get a token&lt;/em&gt; button&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-scrollbar hx-overflow-x-auto hx-overflow-y-hidden hx-overscroll-x-contain&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;hx-mt-4 hx-flex hx-w-max hx-min-w-full hx-border-b hx-border-gray-200 hx-pb-px dark:hx-border-neutral-800&#34;&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34; aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;  tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34;&gt;in a Group Chat&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button
        class=&#34;hextra-tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:hx-border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:hx-text-primary-600 hx-mr-2 hx-rounded-t hx-p-2 hx-font-medium hx-leading-5 hx-transition-colors -hx-mb-0.5 hx-select-none hx-border-b-2 hx-border-transparent hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-border-gray-200 hover:hx-text-black dark:hx-text-gray-200 dark:hover:hx-border-neutral-800 dark:hover:hx-text-white&#34;
        role=&#34;tab&#34;
        type=&#34;button&#34;
        aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;&gt;in a Team&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34; tabindex=&#34;0&#34;  data-state=&#34;selected&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;0010-get-token.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div
  class=&#34;hextra-tabs-panel hx-rounded hx-pt-6 hx-hidden data-[state=selected]:hx-block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;0070-get-a-token.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; style=&#34;margin-left: 0rem&#34;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Step 3: Check your private message&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;step-3-check-your-private-message&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#step-3-check-your-private-message&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bot will send you a private message with the token corresponding to the conversation you clicked the card in.&lt;/p&gt;
